    "name": "More Real than Real",
    "prerequisite": "*Acrobat*, *Celebrity*, *Dandy*, or *Gladiator Dedication*",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "text": "Your performances aren\u2019t just well-known, they\u2019re famous across the land and beyond. Your ability to make people believe the stories you perform has taken on supernatural power. You gain the ability to cast *fabricated truth* once per day as an occult innate spell.",
